data.description: Discover this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home filled with natural light streaming through numerous windows, enhancing the open living space. This home features an open kitchen concept with plenty of cabinet space, granite countertops, stainless-steel appliances, and a beautiful kitchen island. The ample sized primary bedroom offers a walk-in closet and a luxurious ensuite bathroom featuring a walk-in shower with a stylish Roman top. Unwind in the welcoming sunroom and indulge in outdoor gatherings on the fenced patio. Plus, take advantage of the detached efficiency for added living flexibility. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
